# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:12
translate portuguese jamie1_777c0e1d:

    # "I see Jamie leaving her house and walking out towards her car. I wave at her."
    "Vejo a Jamie a sair de casa e a caminhar em direção ao carro. Aceno-lhe."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:15
translate portuguese jamie1_2848acf3:

    # gnd "Hey there."
    gnd "Olá."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:17
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_008.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_008.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:18
translate portuguese jamie1_d7b2148b:

    # gnd "I'm going out for a coffee before class. Want to join me?"
    gnd "Vou tomar um café antes da aula. Queres vir comigo?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:19
translate portuguese jamie1_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Claro."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:20
translate portuguese jamie1_d60e5294:

    # gnd "Do you know where Java Lava is?"
    gnd "Sabes onde fica o Java Lava?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:21
translate portuguese jamie1_6ff82333:

    # pc "Yep."
    pc "Sim."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:23
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice "voices/jamie_006.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_006.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:24
translate portuguese jamie1_55e7809c:

    # gnd "Cool, meet me there."
    gnd "Ótimo, encontramo-nos lá."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:26
translate portuguese jamie1_2d0bcd97:

    # "She smiles and gets into her car before pulling out and heading down the road."
    "Ela sorri e entra no carro antes de arrancar e seguir pela estrada."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:29
translate portuguese jamie1_1da96612:

    # "I get into my car and quickly follow her."
    "Entro no meu carro e sigo-a rapidamente."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:30
translate portuguese jamie1_50a2f2a6:

    # "I wonder why she didn't just want to ride together. It's a little weird since we're coming from pretty much the same place."
    "Pergunto-me porque é que ela não quis simplesmente irmos juntos. É um pouco estranho, já que viemos praticamente do mesmo sítio."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:32
translate portuguese jamie1_f376757c:

    # "I pull into the Java Lava parking lot and can smell the scent of the coffee drifting out of the entire building."
    "Entro no parque de estacionamento do Java Lava e sinto o cheiro do café a espalhar-se por todo o edifício."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:33
translate portuguese jamie1_01e0166e:

    # "I park next to Jamie, who is still sitting in her car."
    "Estaciono ao lado da Jamie, que ainda está sentada no carro."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:34
translate portuguese jamie1_15a1f80d:

    # "She steps out at the same time that I do."
    "Ela sai ao mesmo tempo que eu."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:38
translate portuguese jamie1_32e82c5b:

    # gnd "Hey there, fancy meeting you here."
    gnd "Olá, que surpresa encontrar-te aqui."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:39
translate portuguese jamie1_c2309d17:

    # pc "It is quite a coincidence. Shall we drink together?"
    pc "É uma grande coincidência. Vamos tomar um café juntas?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:40
translate portuguese jamie1_bb6e9df1:

    # gnd "Yes, I think we should."
    gnd "Sim, acho que devíamos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:41
translate portuguese jamie1_bec125c3:

    # "We walk up to the front door together. I hold the door open and the barista greets us as we walk in."
    "Caminhamos juntas até à porta da frente. Seguro a porta aberta e a barista cumprimenta-nos à medida que entramos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:45
translate portuguese jamie1_f6e4b44a:

    # "She looks familiar, but I can't place her. Probably just somebody I've seen around town. It's not a very big place."
    "Ela parece-me familiar, mas não consigo identificá-la. Provavelmente é apenas alguém que já vi pela cidade. Não é um local muito grande."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:47
translate portuguese jamie1_f1d232e2:

    # "Tammy is working again today. I guess she works a lot."
    "A Tammy está a trabalhar outra vez hoje. Acho que ela trabalha muito."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:48
translate portuguese jamie1_e532df5e:

    # "Jamie and I place our orders, and the barista makes them without much small talk."
    "A Jamie e eu fazemos os nossos pedidos, e a barista prepara-os sem muita conversa fiada."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:49
translate portuguese jamie1_4b7ec1d8:

    # "Then we take our drinks and sit across from each other at a small table in the dining area."
    "Depois, pegamos nas nossas bebidas e sentamo-nos frente a frente numa pequena mesa na área de refeições."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:52
translate portuguese jamie1_7ca9f991:

    # "Jamie seems unusually shy. We'd never had a problem talking to each other when we were younger, but things are different now."
    "A Jamie parece invulgarmente tímida. Nunca tivemos problemas em conversar um com o outro quando éramos mais novos, mas agora as coisas são diferentes."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:53
translate portuguese jamie1_e60beee6:

    # "She simply looks at me, and when I look back, she averts her eyes and smiles."
    "Ela limita-se a olhar para mim e, quando olho de volta, ela desvia o olhar e sorri."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:54
translate portuguese jamie1_4d348656:

    # "I don't know what to talk about really."
    "Não sei bem sobre o que falar."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:55
translate portuguese jamie1_3fd979ca:

    # pc "So, you're going to school this semester?"
    pc "Então, vais para a faculdade este semestre?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:56
translate portuguese jamie1_cefd0447:

    # "It seems like an easy question to get us started talking about something."
    "Parece uma pergunta fácil para começarmos a conversar sobre alguma coisa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:58
translate portuguese jamie1_e7bf7de1:

    # gnd "Yeah, Skyhill."
    gnd "Sim, Skyhill."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:59
translate portuguese jamie1_076d61a1:

    # pc "What's your major?"
    pc "Qual é a tua área de especialização?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:60
translate portuguese jamie1_a9ffb9a9:

    # gnd "I'm in the teaching program. I'll be starting my in-class assistant position this semester, where I help a teacher for two periods a day."
    gnd "Estou no curso de pedagogia. Vou começar o meu estágio como assistente de sala de aula este semestre, onde ajudo um professor durante duas aulas por dia."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:61
translate portuguese jamie1_53927809:

    # pc "Oh, that's exciting."
    pc "Oh, isso é emocionante."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:62
translate portuguese jamie1_d7ae6789:

    # gnd "Yeah, I'm pretty nervous about it actually."
    gnd "Sim, na verdade estou bastante nervosa com isso."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:63
translate portuguese jamie1_5924379f:

    # pc "You shouldn't be. You'll do great, I'm sure."
    pc "Não devias estar. Vais sair-te muito bem, tenho a certeza."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:64
translate portuguese jamie1_30b2342d:

    # pc "It doesn't surprise me that you're going to become a teacher."
    pc "Não me surpreende que te venhas a tornar professora."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:65
translate portuguese jamie1_d096758b:

    # pc "You always used to help me with my schoolwork. I don't think I would have passed 8th grade English without your help."
    pc "Costumavas ajudar-me sempre com os trabalhos escolares. Acho que não teria passado a disciplina de Inglês do 8.º ano sem a tua ajuda."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:67
translate portuguese jamie1_8ab7f6ac:

    # gnd "Oh you definitely wouldn't have. Your essays were horrible."
    gnd "Oh, definitivamente não terias passado. As tuas composições eram horríveis."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:68
translate portuguese jamie1_ba5dd62d:

    # pc "They didn't get much better in high school either, or college."
    pc "Também não melhoraram muito no liceu, nem na faculdade."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:70
translate portuguese jamie1_4bc7c623:

    # gnd "So what are you majoring in?"
    gnd "Então, em que te estás a formar?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:71
translate portuguese jamie1_8dfe1fc1:

    # pc "Quantum Science, but I'm having to take all my basics this year, since I didn't take them before."
    pc "Ciência Quântica, mas este ano tenho de fazer todas as disciplinas básicas, já que não as fiz antes."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:72
translate portuguese jamie1_e89ebb70:

    # gnd "Oh cool. Quantum Science, like your dad huh?"
    gnd "Oh, fixe. Ciência Quântica, como o teu pai, não é?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:73
translate portuguese jamie1_73fe1c32:

    # pc "Yeah. Different types, but similar."
    pc "Sim. Tipos diferentes, mas semelhantes."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:74
translate portuguese jamie1_d6a36df7:

    # gnd "I wouldn't have expected that from you."
    gnd "Não esperava isso de ti."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:75
translate portuguese jamie1_d98cce84:

    # pc "Why's that?"
    pc "Porquê?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:76
translate portuguese jamie1_6e902e84:

    # gnd "Well, you never seemed like the type to enjoy the science and math stuff. I always thought that you'd end up being a used car salesman or something."
    gnd "Bem, nunca pareceste ser do tipo que gosta de ciências e matemática. Sempre achei que acabarias por ser vendedor de carros usados ou algo do género."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:77
translate portuguese jamie1_c0131acd:

    # pc "Wow! Harsh!"
    pc "Uau! Que duro!"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:80
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice "voices/jamie_009.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_009.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:81
translate portuguese jamie1_775544cc:

    # gnd "I'm sorry! I didn't mean anything bad by it, I just meant that you were always very charismatic and fast-talking, but never interested in studies."
    gnd "Desculpa! Não quis dizer nada de mal, só quis dizer que sempre foste muito carismático e falas rápido, mas nunca te interessaste por estudos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:82
translate portuguese jamie1_3b20ba0b:

    # gnd "I should have said lawyer - that would have been nicer, I guess. Not that there's anything wrong with used car salesmen though."
    gnd "Devia ter dito advogado — isso teria sido melhor, acho eu. Não que haja algo de errado com vendedores de carros usados, claro."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:83
translate portuguese jamie1_d28b9880:

    # pc "Well I'm a lot different than I was when I was 13."
    pc "Bem, sou muito diferente do que era quando tinha 13 anos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:86
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_3:

    # voice "voices/jamie_054.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_054.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:87
translate portuguese jamie1_59601283:

    # gnd "Speaking of when we were 13, there was something I wanted to ask you."
    gnd "Por falar em quando tínhamos 13 anos, havia uma coisa que queria perguntar-te."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:88
translate portuguese jamie1_88fa21e7:

    # pc "Ask away."
    pc "Pergunta à vontade."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:90
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_4:

    # voice "voices/jamie_055.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_055.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:92
translate portuguese jamie1_7520d05b:

    # gnd "Why did you break up with me?"
    gnd "Porque é que terminaste comigo?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:93
translate portuguese jamie1_7eba9d8e:

    # "My stomach does a sort of backflip. This is not what I had been expecting at all."
    "O meu estômago dá uma espécie de cambalhota. Isto não é nada do que eu esperava."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:94
translate portuguese jamie1_b464fd63:

    # pc "Break up with you? What do you mean?"
    pc "Terminar contigo? O que queres dizer?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:97
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_5:

    # voice "voices/jamie_056.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_056.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:98
translate portuguese jamie1_208f93af:

    # gnd "In middle school. We had been neighbors and friends for pretty much our whole lives."
    gnd "No ensino básico. Fomos vizinhos e amigos praticamente toda a nossa vida."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:100
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_6:

    # voice "voices/jamie_057.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_057.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:101
translate portuguese jamie1_03b1922c:

    # gnd "We'd play at each other's houses. You were my first kiss. You were the first boy to touch my boobs, although there wasn't much there at the time."
    gnd "Brincávamos nas casas um do outro. Foste o meu primeiro beijo. Foste o primeiro rapaz a tocar-me nos seios, embora na altura não houvesse grande coisa lá."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:104
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_7:

    # voice "voices/jamie_058.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_058.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:105
translate portuguese jamie1_d37ad228:

    # gnd "We went to Homecoming together. Remember?"
    gnd "Fomos juntos ao baile de finalistas. Lembras-te?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:108
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_8:

    # voice "voices/jamie_059.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_059.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:109
translate portuguese jamie1_a5fe0c77:

    # gnd "Then, out of nowhere, you just stopped talking to me."
    gnd "Depois, do nada, deixaste de falar comigo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:111
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_060.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_060.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:112
translate portuguese jamie1_a94569ad:

    # gnd "You didn't come over and see me anymore, you didn't answer my phone calls, you didn't even acknowledge me in the halls at school."
    gnd "Deixaste de vir visitar-me, não atendias as minhas chamadas, nem sequer me cumprimentavas nos corredores da escola."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:113
translate portuguese jamie1_60a987f0:

    # pc "Wait, what? I don't remember doing any of that."
    pc "Espera, o quê? Não me lembro de ter feito nada disso."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:114
translate portuguese jamie1_7d86fb5a:

    # pc "We just stopped hanging out together. You had different friends and so did I."
    pc "Simplesmente deixámos de sair juntos. Tu tinhas outros amigos e eu também."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:116
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_10:

    # voice "voices/jamie_061.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_061.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:117
translate portuguese jamie1_dc86cca2:

    # gnd "Is that what you think happened?"
    gnd "É isso que achas que aconteceu?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:118
translate portuguese jamie1_69b6e4a8:

    # pc "From what I remember. That was a long time ago."
    pc "Pelo que me lembro. Isso foi há muito tempo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:120
translate portuguese jamie1_58fea4ec:

    # "She sighs and looks away from me, her bottom lip sticking out. My response obviously made her upset, but I truly don't remember things happening that way."
    "Ela suspira e desvia o olhar de mim, com o lábio inferior de fora. A minha resposta obviamente a deixou chateada, mas eu sinceramente não me lembro das coisas terem acontecido dessa forma."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:121
translate portuguese jamie1_a62cc161:

    # "I did stop going over to her house, but that was just because we stopped hanging out as much."
    "Eu deixei de ir a casa dela, mas isso foi apenas porque deixámos de sair tanto juntas."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:122
translate portuguese jamie1_3ad28c2d:

    # "I might have ignored some of her phone calls, but I don't think it was intentional. I was just doing other things and it slipped my mind."
    "Posso ter ignorado algumas das chamadas dela, mas não acho que tenha sido intencional. Estava apenas ocupado com outras coisas e isso escapou-me da cabeça."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:123
translate portuguese jamie1_7e6fa894:

    # "And I didn't greet everybody I knew in the halls every time we passed - that's just silly."
    "E não cumprimentava toda a gente que conhecia nos corredores sempre que nos cruzávamos — isso é simplesmente ridículo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:124
translate portuguese jamie1_515956f7:

    # "But there is something else. I do remember being upset at her about something. Maybe I did consciously ignore her?"
    "Mas há outra coisa. Lembro-me de estar chateado com ela por causa de alguma coisa. Talvez a tenha ignorado conscientemente?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:127
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_11:

    # voice "voices/jamie_062.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_062.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:128
translate portuguese jamie1_dce96005:

    # gnd "It wasn't just the normal growing apart. Something happened, and you just cut me off completely."
    gnd "Não foi apenas o afastamento normal que acontece quando se cresce. Algo aconteceu e tu simplesmente afastaste-te de mim completamente."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:130
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_12:

    # voice "voices/jamie_063.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_063.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:131
translate portuguese jamie1_98593801:

    # gnd "Every time I tried to ask you why, you blew me off, until eventually I just got the hint that you didn't like me anymore."
    gnd "Sempre que tentava perguntar-te porquê, tu ignoravas-me, até que, eventualmente, percebi que já não gostavas de mim."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:132
translate portuguese jamie1_306adf54:

    # pc "I didn't stop liking--"
    pc "Eu não deixei de gostar..."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:134
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_13:

    # voice "voices/jamie_064.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_064.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:135
translate portuguese jamie1_02d938ef:

    # gnd "It was right after that Homecoming dance. We had a good time there. I know we did."
    gnd "Foi logo a seguir ao baile de boas-vindas. Divertimo-nos lá. Eu sei que sim."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:137
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_14:

    # voice "voices/jamie_065.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_065.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:138
translate portuguese jamie1_b0be8140:

    # gnd "We danced like middle school kids, just holding each other and swaying back and forth."
    gnd "Dançámos como miúdos do ensino básico, apenas abraçados e a balançar para a frente e para trás."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:140
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_15:

    # voice "voices/jamie_066.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_066.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:141
translate portuguese jamie1_7107383b:

    # gnd "Then we snuck off to the corner and made out for the rest of the night."
    gnd "Depois, esgueirámo-nos para um canto e ficámos a beijar-nos o resto da noite."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:143
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_16:

    # voice "voices/jamie_067.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_067.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:144
translate portuguese jamie1_6e0d44b1:

    # gnd "Afterwards, I thought I did something wrong. That you didn't like kissing me or something. That I had made you mad."
    gnd "Depois disso, pensei que tinha feito algo de errado. Que não gostavas de me beijar ou algo assim. Que te tinha irritado."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:146
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_17:

    # voice "voices/jamie_068.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_068.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:147
translate portuguese jamie1_ae5a2abe:

    # gnd "So what was it? What happened?"
    gnd "Então, o que foi? O que aconteceu?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:148
translate portuguese jamie1_820e82ce:

    # pc "Homecoming? That was 8th grade?"
    pc "O baile de boas-vindas? Isso foi no 8.º ano?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:149
translate portuguese jamie1_5c9ff614:

    # "She nods."
    "Ela acena com a cabeça."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:150
translate portuguese jamie1_dab6ae1d:

    # pc "Ugh. I remember now."
    pc "Ugh. Agora lembro-me."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:152
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_18:

    # voice "voices/jamie_069.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_069.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:153
translate portuguese jamie1_27030523:

    # gnd "Oh really?"
    gnd "A sério?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:154
translate portuguese jamie1_791da015:

    # pc "Do you remember my friend Tosh?"
    pc "Lembras-te do meu amigo Tosh?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:156
translate portuguese jamie1_3b8202ee:

    # "She nods again."
    "Ela acena com a cabeça outra vez."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:157
translate portuguese jamie1_35a1b275:

    # pc "Well we were best friends at the time. We rode bikes everywhere and played video games together."
    pc "Bem, nós éramos melhores amigos na altura. Andávamos de bicicleta para todo o lado e jogávamos videojogos juntos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:159
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_19:

    # voice "voices/jamie_070.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_070.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:160
translate portuguese jamie1_5dcba36c:

    # gnd "I remember. You kind of stopped hanging out with me as much once he started coming around."
    gnd "Lembro-me. Tu deixaste de sair tanto comigo assim que ele começou a aparecer."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:161
translate portuguese jamie1_d2697e62:

    # pc "Yeah, well after the Homecoming dance, he told me that he heard you saying stuff in the Spanish class that you shared with him."
    pc "Sim, bem, depois do baile de boas-vindas, ele disse-me que te tinha ouvido a dizer coisas na aula de espanhol que tu partilhavas com ele."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:162
translate portuguese jamie1_09200a36:

    # pc "Stuff like that you didn't really like me and that you only went to the dance with me because I gave you chocolates and flowers and stuff."
    pc "Coisas do tipo que tu não gostavas mesmo de mim e que só foste ao baile comigo porque eu te dei chocolates e flores e coisas assim."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:165
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_20:

    # voice "voices/jamie_071.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_071.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:166
translate portuguese jamie1_9a75f2cb:

    # gnd "That's ridiculous! I never said anything like that!"
    gnd "Isso é ridículo! Eu nunca disse nada disso!"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:167
translate portuguese jamie1_358eaba7:

    # pc "I believe you!"
    pc "Acredito em ti!"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:168
translate portuguese jamie1_9638be50:

    # pc "But at the time, I thought that Tosh was completely honest, and I trusted everything he said."
    pc "Mas na altura, achava que o Tosh era completamente honesto e confiava em tudo o que ele dizia."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:169
translate portuguese jamie1_89d02a73:

    # pc "It wasn't until high school that I realized that he was completely full of shit."
    pc "Só no liceu é que percebi que ele era um grande mentiroso."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:170
translate portuguese jamie1_b50f91a5:

    # pc "I think he's in jail now."
    pc "Acho que ele está na prisão agora."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:173
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_21:

    # voice "voices/jamie_072.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_072.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:174
translate portuguese jamie1_11f27db5:

    # gnd "So that's it? We were friends our whole lives, but you trusted some new guy friend from school and didn't even talk to me about it? Didn't even let me defend myself?"
    gnd "Então é isso? Fomos amigos a vida toda, mas confiaste num amigo novo da escola e nem sequer falaste comigo sobre isso? Nem sequer me deixaste defender-me?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:178
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_22:

    # voice "voices/jamie_073.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_073.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:179
translate portuguese jamie1_4975276b:

    # gnd "Hell yes, you were."
    gnd "Claro que sim, estavas."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:182
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_23:

    # voice "voices/jamie_074.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_074.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:183
translate portuguese jamie1_4e3ae829:

    # gnd "What does it matter?"
    gnd "O que importa isso?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:185
translate portuguese jamie1_9872e61d:

    # "She looks at me, tears pooling in her eyes."
    "Ela olha para mim, com lágrimas a acumularem-se nos olhos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:187
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_24:

    # voice "voices/jamie_075.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_075.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:188
translate portuguese jamie1_1692a6fc:

    # gnd "You broke my heart. I know it's all middle school stuff, but you'd be surprised how much things that happen during that time in your life affect your mindset."
    gnd "Partiste-me o coração. Sei que são coisas do ensino básico, mas ficarias surpreendido com o quanto as coisas que acontecem nessa fase da vida afetam a tua mentalidade."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:190
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_25:

    # voice "voices/jamie_076.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_076.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:191
translate portuguese jamie1_76ad11a6:

    # gnd "I was so in love with you, you wouldn't believe it."
    gnd "Eu estava tão apaixonada por ti que nem acreditas."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:193
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_26:

    # voice "voices/jamie_077.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_077.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:194
translate portuguese jamie1_e649708c:

    # gnd "You cutting me off like that sort of flipped a switch in my brain."
    gnd "O facto de me teres afastado assim foi como se tivesse ligado um interruptor no meu cérebro."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:196
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_27:

    # voice "voices/jamie_078.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_078.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:197
translate portuguese jamie1_42cafbea:

    # gnd "I shut down for a long time. I didn't trust people, didn't make friends easily."
    gnd "Fiquei fechada em mim durante muito tempo. Não confiava nas pessoas, não fazia amigos facilmente."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:199
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_28:

    # voice "voices/jamie_079.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_079.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:200
translate portuguese jamie1_58eb925b:

    # gnd "I mostly just laid in my room and studied and cried."
    gnd "Passava a maior parte do tempo deitada no meu quarto, a estudar e a chorar."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:202
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_29:

    # voice "voices/jamie_080.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_080.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:203
translate portuguese jamie1_f2e0045e:

    # gnd "That's why my dad hates you. He saw what you did to me and he's never forgiven you for it."
    gnd "É por isso que o meu pai te odeia. Ele viu o que me fizeste e nunca te perdoou por isso."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:206
translate portuguese jamie1_10be1c3b:

    # pc "I'm so sorry. I was a stupid kid, but that's no excuse."
    pc "Peço imensa desculpa. Eu era uma miúda estúpida, mas isso não é desculpa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:207
translate portuguese jamie1_bcb802d4:

    # pc "I should have never treated you like that."
    pc "Nunca te devia ter tratado assim."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:209
translate portuguese jamie1_76abefbc:

    # pc "I'm not going to apologize for stuff I did when I was 13 years old. I was a stupid kid. All kids are stupid kids."
    pc "Não vou pedir desculpa por coisas que fiz quando tinha 13 anos. Eu era uma miúda estúpida. Todas as miúdas são estúpidas."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:212
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_30:

    # voice "voices/jamie_081.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_081.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:213
translate portuguese jamie1_326ba1f0:

    # gnd "You're STILL a stupid kid! I'm done here! This was a mistake! We're not friends, don't talk to me anymore!"
    gnd "Tu AINDA és uma miúda estúpida! Estou farta disto! Isto foi um erro! Não somos amigas, não voltes a falar comigo!"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:214
translate portuguese jamie1_6ca9d573:

    # "With that, she stands up and walks out of the café."
    "Dito isto, ela levanta-se e sai do café."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:215
translate portuguese jamie1_01c3f816:

    # "Others avert their gaze from me, trying to pretend that they hadn't heard what just happened."
    "Os outros desviam o olhar de mim, tentando fingir que não ouviram o que acabou de acontecer."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:216
translate portuguese jamie1_f5d0b218:

    # "This had not gone anything like what I had wanted. I'm not sure if my relationship with Jamie is even salvageable now."
    "Isto não correu nada como eu queria. Não sei se a minha relação com a Jamie ainda tem salvação."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:217
translate portuguese jamie1_a686ffdc:

    # "I finish up my coffee, thinking about the mistakes I'd made, then I head back out to the car and go to school."
    "Termino o meu café, a pensar nos erros que cometi, depois volto para o carro e vou para a escola."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:223
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_31:

    # voice "voices/jamie_082.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_082.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:224
translate portuguese jamie1_4d43b439:

    # gnd "You have no idea how long I've dreamed about hearing you say that."
    gnd "Não fazes ideia de há quanto tempo sonhava em ouvir-te dizer isso."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:226
translate portuguese jamie1_b94d1a33:

    # "She takes a deep breath, then reaches across the table and puts her hands on top of mine."
    "Ela respira fundo, depois estende a mão por cima da mesa e coloca as mãos sobre as minhas."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:229
translate portuguese jamie1_d41d8cd9_32:

    # voice "voices/jamie_083.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_083.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:230
translate portuguese jamie1_fa010ee6:

    # gnd "I forgive you."
    gnd "Eu perdoo-te."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:231
translate portuguese jamie1_521ec7fb:

    # pc "Thank you. I want to be friends again. Can we start over?"
    pc "Obrigado. Quero que voltemos a ser amigos. Podemos recomeçar?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:233
translate portuguese jamie1_07ca4578:

    # gnd "I don't think there's such a thing as starting over, but we can start working on repairing the damage."
    gnd "Acho que não existe isso de recomeçar, mas podemos começar a trabalhar para reparar os danos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:235
translate portuguese jamie1_88df1b89:

    # gnd "This helped a lot."
    gnd "Isto ajudou muito."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:236
translate portuguese jamie1_ab6c009b:

    # pc "I'm glad. We should do it again."
    pc "Ainda bem. Devíamos repetir isto."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:237
translate portuguese jamie1_241ea26c:

    # gnd "Definitely. With hopefully less crying."
    gnd "Sem dúvida. Com menos lágrimas, espero."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:238
translate portuguese jamie1_c8d9b24c:

    # "We finish up our coffees and walk out to the cars together."
    "Terminamos os nossos cafés e caminhamos juntas até aos carros."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:241
translate portuguese jamie1_1b15168b:

    # gnd "Text me sometime, we can go get coffee again or something."
    gnd "Manda-me uma mensagem um dia destes, podemos ir tomar café outra vez ou algo do género."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:242
translate portuguese jamie1_9b5f710f:

    # pc "I will, I promise."
    pc "Vou mandar, prometo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:244
translate portuguese jamie1_d311130c:

    # gnd "Thanks for this."
    gnd "Obrigada por isto."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:245
translate portuguese jamie1_ca03cbd8:

    # pc "No, I should be thanking you for giving me another chance."
    pc "Não, sou eu que te devo agradecer por me dares outra oportunidade."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:246
translate portuguese jamie1_861e750f:

    # pc "I'm not going to hurt you again, I promise. I'm not the same person I was then."
    pc "Não te vou magoar outra vez, prometo. Já não sou a mesma pessoa que era naquela altura."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:247
translate portuguese jamie1_18b10010:

    # gnd "I know. I can tell."
    gnd "Eu sei. Dá para ver."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:249
translate portuguese jamie1_1c4e0503:

    # gnd "I'll see you later."
    gnd "Até logo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:250
translate portuguese jamie1_d22c868b:

    # "She gets into her car and drives away, back towards her house."
    "Ela entra no carro e parte, de volta para casa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:252
translate portuguese jamie1_3aaaf55b:

    # "The coffee date hadn't gone anything like I expected it too, but I am still happy with the outcome."
    "O encontro para tomar café não correu nada como eu esperava, mas ainda assim estou contente com o resultado."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:253
translate portuguese jamie1_d14d202f:

    # "Now that everything is out in the open, It feels like I have a real connection with Jamie."
    "Agora que tudo está à vista, sinto que tenho uma ligação verdadeira com a Jamie."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:254
translate portuguese jamie1_1cc92515:

    # "I want to treat her right and earn her forgiveness."
    "Quero tratá-la bem e merecer o seu perdão."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:255
translate portuguese jamie1_26a71157:

    # "If anything else comes after that, great, but I don't expect it. Not after the way I had treated her."
    "Se acontecer mais alguma coisa depois disso, ótimo, mas não estou à espera. Não depois da forma como a tratei."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:256
translate portuguese jamie1_86fdd457:

    # "I get into the car and drive away."
    "Entro no carro e vou-me embora."

